T1  - SPOUSAL LABOR SUPPLY, CAREGIVING, AND THE VALUE OF DISABILITY INSURANCE
AU  - Lee, Siha
Y1  - 2024/11/01
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2024/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12712
T2  - International Economic Review
